            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Cost Optimization</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Reduce IT costs through better service management, improved efficiency, and strategic resource allocation.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
