        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">ISO/IEC 20000-1 Implementation Process</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Structured approach to implementing comprehensive IT Service Management System (SMS).
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Current State Assessment</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Evaluate existing IT service management processes and identify improvement opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
